OL,3,CThree men convicted of attempt murder
OL,4,Cafter shots fired in Perry Barr
OL,6,FThree men have been convicted of
OL,7,Fattempted murder after shots were
OL,8,Ffired in Perry Barr, in Birmingham,
OL,9,Fearlier this year.
OL,11,FIt happened at an address in Glendower
OL,12,FRoad at around 11pm on 18 May. Three
OL,13,Fshots were fired in quick succession,
OL,14,Ftargeting the upstairs and downstairs
OL,15,Fwindows of the property.
OL,17,FPolice said the final bullet struck a
OL,18,Fwindow which caused the glass to
OL,19,Fshatter. A man in his 60s, who was in
OL,20,Fthe property at the time, was injured
OL,21,Fby the broken glass.
