OL,3,CThree men convicted of attempt murder
OL,4,Cafter shots fired in Perry Barr
OL,6,FDuring the shooting, a camera at the
OL,7,Ffront of the address was damaged in
OL,8,Fattempt to conceal the identities of
OL,9,Fthe offenders. A brick was also thrown
OL,10,Fat the windscreen of a parked car near
OL,11,Fthe property.
OL,13,FOfficers said the offenders then drove
OL,14,Foff from the scene in a stolen Skoda
OL,15,Fvehicle and burned the car, destroying
OL,16,Fevidence.
