OL,3,CThree men convicted of attempt murder
OL,4,Cafter shots fired in Perry Barr
OL,6,FThe police investigation was based on
OL,7,FCCTV footage, ANPR cameras and mobile
OL,8,Fphone evidence which allowed them to
OL,9,Fpiece together a timeline of events in
OL,10,Fthe build up to the shooting.
OL,12,FThis led officers to identify three
OL,13,Foffenders who targeted the victim's
OL,14,Faddress in a planned attack - Shomari
OL,15,FMapp aged 22, Aairus Rehman aged 22
OL,16,Fand Shaquon Richardson-Bowen aged 21.
