OL,3,CThree men convicted of attempt murder
OL,4,Cafter shots fired in Perry Barr
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Francis Nock, from
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police's Major Crimes
OL,8,FUnit, said: "This was a planned and
OL,9,Ftargeted attack on a family home when
OL,10,Fthe gang knew the occupiers would be
OL,11,Fat the address.
OL,13,F"The shooting required immense
OL,14,Fplanning such as a reccy of the area,
OL,15,Fsignificant communication between the
OL,16,Fgroup, and covering their tracks.
OL,18,F"It's a miracle someone wasn't more
OL,19,Fseriously injured."
