OL,3,CThree men convicted of attempt murder
OL,4,Cafter shots fired in Perry Barr
OL,6,FIn the hours leading up to the
OL,7,Fshooting, mobile phone evidence shows
OL,8,Fall three men were together or in
OL,9,Fclose proximity. Their mobile phones
OL,10,Fwere all then switched off or inactive
OL,11,Fduring the shooting.
OL,13,FCCTV footage shows the gang driving
OL,14,Fpast Glendower Road, an hour before
OL,15,Fthe shooting to survey the area.
OL,17,FFollowing enquiries, all three men
OL,18,Fwere arrested and subsequently charged.
