OL,3,CThree men convicted of attempt murder
OL,4,Cafter shots fired in Perry Barr
OL,6,FAfter a trial at Birmingham Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Mapp of Melvina Road,
OL,8,FBirmingham and Richardson-Bowen of
OL,9,FSeverne Road, Birmingham have been
OL,10,Fconvicted of attempt murder and arson.
OL,12,FRehman of Ringlow Road, Birmingham,
OL,13,Fadmitted to arson and possession of a
OL,14,Ffirearm with intent to endanger life
OL,15,Fat an earlier hearing, and was found
OL,16,Fguilty at trial for attempt murder.
OL,18,FThey are scheduled to be sentenced on
OL,19,F29 January next year.
